challenges: High failure rate on image downloads (75% of discovered URLs failed)
Wikimedia API rate limiting and intermittent 403 errors
Category structure inconsistencies - some categories returned 0 results
URL format variations causing download failures

key_insights.images_discovered: Approximately 470 unique images found via API

recommendations: Use Wikimedia Commons dump files for bulk extraction instead of API
Implement more robust retry logic with exponential backoff
Use multiple User-Agent rotation to avoid blocks
Consider using Commons API with OAuth for higher rate limits
Download from Internet Archive mirrors for better reliability
